So the question comes up,

00:15:24.659 --> 00:15:27.860
what part of the dialogue was actually stated

00:15:27.860 --> 00:15:30.100
here in the synagogue in Capernaum,

00:15:30.100 --> 00:15:32.860
and what part was stated along the sea shore

00:15:32.860 --> 00:15:34.620
as he was walking along?

