So we'll have to do some research into John Chapter 6

00:15:38.419 --> 00:15:41.940
and see where is a good break for us to realize

00:15:41.980 --> 00:15:44.940
what words were actually said there in the synagogue.

00:15:44.940 --> 00:15:46.220
That's the challenge.

00:15:46.220 --> 00:15:48.820
We need for the friends to be able to watch

00:15:48.820 --> 00:15:52.899
this video series and feel they're actually there.

00:15:52.899 --> 00:15:55.299
And what they are seeing is as close to the way

00:15:55.299 --> 00:15:57.779
it must have been as we can possibly make it.

00:15:57.779 --> 00:16:01.019
And the role of research helps us to ensure that.

