00:16:42.179 --> 00:16:45.100
so that on set, the challenges don't just pop up,

00:16:45.100 --> 00:16:48.500
you can anticipate them.

00:16:48.500 --> 00:16:50.580
Concept art is a communication tool

00:16:50.580 --> 00:16:52.820
to help us to get all in the same page.

00:16:53.980 --> 00:16:58.620
Concept art helps us to get the mood of it, the lighting,

00:16:58.620 --> 00:17:01.220
to experience it maybe from a perspective

00:17:01.220 --> 00:17:03.019
that we hadn't thought of it before.

00:17:04.380 --> 00:17:08.059
The story of Jesus' ministry isn't just dry, cold facts.

00:17:08.059 --> 00:17:10.380
